# Tailwind CSS Styles

## Design Tokens

```css
/* globals.css */
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;

:root {
  --color-primary: #111111;
}
```

## Color Classes

| Purpose | Class | Value |
|---|---|---|
| Primary text/buttons | `text-primary`, `bg-primary` | `#111111` |
| White backgrounds | `bg-white` | `#ffffff` |
| Gray borders | `border`, `border-gray-200` | `#e5e7eb` |
| Gray text | `text-gray-500`, `text-gray-600` | varies |
| Gray backgrounds | `bg-gray-50`, `bg-gray-100` | varies |
| Red error | `text-red-500`, `bg-red-50` | varies |
| Green success | `bg-green-100`, `text-green-700` | varies |

## Typography

| Element | Classes |
|---|---|
| Page title | `text-3xl font-bold mb-8` |
| Section title | `text-2xl font-bold mb-6` |
| Card title | `font-semibold` |
| Body text | `text-gray-600`, `text-gray-500` |
| Price | `font-bold text-primary` |
| Button text | `text-white`, `text-sm` |

## Spacing & Layout

| Pattern | Classes |
|---|---|
| Page container | `max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4` |
| Card grid | `grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6` |
| Section padding | `py-12`, `py-16`, `py-20` |
| Card padding | `p-4`, `p-6` |
| Form gap | `flex flex-col gap-3`, `flex flex-col gap-4` |

## Component Styles

### Header
```tsx
<header className="border-b">
  <nav className="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
    {/* nav items */}
  </nav>
</header>
```

### Footer
```tsx
<footer className="border-t mt-auto">
  <div className="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    {/* footer content */}
  </div>
</footer>
```

### Card
```tsx
<div className="border rounded-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
  {/* card content */}
</div>
```

### Button Primary
```tsx
<button className="bg-black text-white px-4 py-2 rounded cursor-pointer transition-colors hover:bg-gray-800 disabled:opacity-50">
```

### Button Secondary
```tsx
<button className="border px-4 py-2 rounded cursor-pointer transition-colors hover:bg-gray-50">
```

### Form Input
```tsx
<input type="text" className="border px-3 py-2 rounded" />
```

### Modal Overlay
```tsx
<div className="fixed inset-0 bg-black/50 flex items-center justify-center z-50">
  <div className="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 w-full max-w-lg">
```

### Table
```tsx
<table className="w-full border-collapse">
  <thead><tr className="border-b"><th className="text-left py-2"></th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>{rows.map(r => <tr key={r.id} className="border-b hover:bg-gray-50"><td className="py-3"></td></tr>)}</tbody>
</table>
```

## Animation & Transitions

- Hover transitions: `transition-colors`, `transition-shadow`
- Spinner: `animate-spin h-8 w-8 border-4 border-black border-t-transparent rounded-full`
- Scroll: `overflow-y-auto`
- Fade (mobile nav): opacity transition on conditional render
